[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michael Duckworth: Morecambe sign Fleetwood Town defender on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Morecambe have signed Fleetwood defender Michael Duckworth on loan until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 24-year-old joined the Cod Army from Hartlepool in June 2016 but has made just four league appearances this season.
He spent three seasons with Pools, scoring three times in 80 league games.
Duckworth, who can also play in midfield, could make his debut for the Shrimps against League Two leaders Doncaster on Saturday.
